      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to fall in love with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously cared for, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare find for anyone seeking perfection and peak performance in their next ride!",
