    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a great opportunity for an enthusiast looking for a solid project or a budget-friendly entry into this model. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some clear coat fading on the roof and trunk, and a few small dings consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all gauges and basic electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but a thorough tune-up and some suspension work would be beneficial to bring it back to its best. It\u2019s an honest car with plenty of life left for someone willing to put in a little work.",
      "price": 19800.0,
