      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and has been pampered every single mile. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
