    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8 powerplant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a 6-speed manual transmission with precise gate engagement and a Variable M Differential Lock that ensures optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally pristine, showing no signs of subframe stress, and the suspension geometry is maintained by factory Electronic Damping Control (EDC). Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings and new throttle actuators, ensuring the S65\u2019s 8,400 RPM redline is reached with total reliability. The exterior retains factory-spec paint depth across all panels, while the cabin features impeccable Novillo leather with no bolster compression. This is a definitive collector-tier example of the last naturally aspirated V8 M-car",
      "price": 50000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
