    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirls, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather seats retain their original matte finish and scent, with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing. Every button, screen, and switch operates with the crisp tactile feedback of a brand-new car. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained strictly by the book with a full, documented service history. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the meticulous care this car has received. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
